The street, teeming with life, stretches out below, lined with trees that add a touch of green to the urban landscape. Cars of various colors are scattered along the road, their metallic bodies gleaming under the sunlight. Buildings of different heights and designs flank the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. The sky above is a clear blue, with a smattering of clouds adding depth to the expansive sky. The image is framed by trees on either side, their leaves forming a natural border to the urban expanse.
